<center><a href=""><span class="title">Wp Plugin Comment Highlighter</span></a></center>

<h3><u>Plugin Details</u></h3><div>Plugin Name: <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/comment-highlighter/" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow" target="_blank">wp-plugin : comment-highlighter</a></div>
<div>Effected Version : 0.13 (and most probably lower version's if any)</div>
<div>Vulnerability : <a href="/category/injection/">Injection</a></div>
<div>Minimum Level of Access Required : Administrator</div>
<div>CVE Number : CVE-2021-24393</div>
<div>Identified by : <a href="/author/syed_sheeraz_ali/">Syed Sheeraz Ali</a></div>
<div><a href="https://wpscan.com/plugin/comment-highlighter/" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow" target="_blank">WPScan Reference URL</a></div>
 
<h3><u>Disclosure Timeline</u></h3>
<ul>
	<li>

<div>May 9, 2021: Issue Identified and Disclosed to WPScan</div>

	</li>
	
	<li>
	June 10, 2021 : Plugin  Closed</li>
	
	
	<li>June 10, 2021 : CVE Assigned</li>
	
	<li>July 23, 2021 : Public Disclosure</li>
</ul>



<h3><u>Technical Details</u></h3>

<p>Vulnerable File: <code>admin/section/swiftbook-add-email-templates.php#30</code></p>
<p>Vulnerable Code block and parameter:</p>
<p>Administrator level SQLi for parameter <code>c</code> <a href="https://plugins.trac.wordpress.org/browser/comment-highlighter/trunk/comment_highlighter.php#252" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">/comment_highlighter.php#252</a>
</p>
<pre><code>252:            $_meta  = $wpdb-&gt;get_row ( &quot;SELECT * FROM {$wpdb-&gt;comments} WHERE comment_ID = {$_GET['c']};&quot; ) ;
